title: Wahoo's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A "surf" tacos & Mexican fast food food chain. The menu offers different filling choices for tacos, burritos, enchiladas, and bowls. Veg filling include marinated tofu, saute mixed vegetable teriyaki, or vegetarian rice and bean (has cheese). Vegans must specify; otherwise you might get cheese/dairy in your order. Note the white rice contains butter but the brown rice does not.
